title: Feeling Drained
entry: Woke up feeling exhausted again. Even after a full night's sleep, I still feel tired.

title: Lack of Motivation
entry: I have so much to do, but I just can't bring myself to start. Everything feels overwhelming.

title: Mind Feels Foggy
entry: I can't concentrate on anything. My thoughts are scattered, and I feel unproductive.

title: Social Disconnect
entry: I haven't talked to any of my friends in days. I feel like I'm isolating myself again.

title: Anxiety at Work
entry: The thought of work tomorrow is making me anxious. I don't know how to get through it.

title: Trying to Ground Myself
entry: I read about the 5-4-3-2-1 technique today. Maybe I should try it to calm down.

title: Overthinking Conversations
entry: I keep replaying a conversation from yesterday. Did I say something weird? Did they think I was awkward?

title: Deep Breaths
entry: I tried deep breathing exercises today. It helped a little, but my mind still races too much.

title: Drowning in Procrastination
entry: I have an important task to complete, but I'm avoiding it. The more I wait, the worse it gets.

title: Two-Minute Rule Attempt
entry: I decided to try the two-minute rule. I told myself I’d just open the document, and somehow I ended up working for 20 minutes.

title: Loneliness Hits Hard
entry: I feel invisible. No messages, no calls. Maybe I should reach out first, but I don't want to bother anyone.

title: Thinking About Old Friends
entry: I miss how easy things used to be. I used to have people to talk to, now it just feels empty.

title: Heart Still Hurts
entry: I thought I was okay, but seeing something that reminded me of my ex hit me hard today.

title: Trying Not to Stalk Social Media
entry: I promised myself I wouldn’t check their profile today. I almost did, but I stopped myself.

title: Career Doubts
entry: I don’t know if I’m in the right field. What if I’m wasting time?

title: Revisiting My Passion
entry: I used to love writing. Maybe I should start again, just for myself.
